  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Then the Germans-- they created the-- Jewish student can no longer attend public schools.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were told by our teachers, who were very sympathetic, that we can no longer go to school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that time also, my sister's tutor, whom we called Mietec, who was in the Polish army-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] contacted my sister.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they decided that he has to run away for Poland, not as Jew at this time, but as a Polish officer who deserted-- not deserted, but who had to run away, you know, not to fall into the German hands.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister and my not-yet brother-in-law left for four East Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were left, my parents, my sister, Estuscha, and I, at home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Of course, because there was no electricity and there was no water, the factory was closed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if I mentioned to you that my father had a factory of hand-carved wooden objects.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he couldn't-- the factory was closed as soon as the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By my father.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It could no longer function.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What my father did, he took-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] wooden post cards from the First World War.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used to have a little tray and sell it in the cafes where the Germans were sitting to get some money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at this point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother-in-law came back from East Poland, and he was trying to talk my parents into leaving with him to East Poland, telling them that--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Telling them that the Germans are going to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] make great difficulties to the Jews, that we're not safe where we were.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
